VOTABLE.DESCRIPTION:
ROSAT was an orbiting x-ray observatory active in the 1990s. We provide a table of all photons observed during ROSAT's all-sky survey (RASS) as well as images of both survey and pointed observations.
For ROSAT data products, see http://www.xray.mpe.mpg.de/cgi-bin/rosat/rosat-survey

RESOURCE.INFO: This resource contains data associated with the publication 2000IAUC.7432R...1V.
For advice on how to cite the resource(s) that contributed to this result, see http://dc.zah.uni-heidelberg.de/tableinfo/rosat.photons

TABLE.name: ndtmwngpwgpa
TABLE.DESCRIPTION: A table of x-ray photons detected by ROSAT

FIELD.name: detection_time
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Time the photon was detected, in Julian years.

FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Photon identifier (a combination of observation date and detector coordinates)
